BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Open Application / File / Apple Script â€¦
Open Native OS X Split View for Window (Left)
Restore Old Window Size
Resize window to Right Two Thirds
Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: set asrc to "BRAGI HP 16"tell application "System Preferences"	reveal anchor "output" of pane id "com.apple.preference.sound"	activate		tell application "System Events"		tell process "System Preferences"			select (row 1 of table 1 of scroll area 1 of tab group 1 of window "Sound" whose value of text field 1 is asrc)		end tell	end tell	quitend telldisplay notification "Output Device: " & asrc

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Maximize Window
Open Native OS X Split View for Window (Right)
Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: tell application "Google Chrome"	activate	if (count of windows) is 0 or front window is not visible then		make new window	else		make new tab at end of tabs of front window	end ifend tell

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Resize window to Middle Third
Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: set search_url to "https://www.youtube.com"set open_url to "https://www.youtube.com"tell application "Google Chrome"	activate	repeat with w in windows		set i to 1		repeat with t in tabs of w			if URL of t starts with search_url then				set active tab index of w to i				set index of w to 1				return			end if			set i to i + 1		end repeat	end repeat	open location open_urlend tell

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: set tab_url to "https://www.youtube.com/"set return_text to "Now Playing"if application "Google Chrome" is running then	tell application "Google Chrome"		repeat with w in windows			set i to 1			repeat with t in tabs of w				if URL of t starts with tab_url then					return return_text				end if				set i to i + 1			end repeat		end repeat		return ""	end tellelse	return ""end if
